Package project

All the classes relating to the OOP project
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    The general base class for all accounts
    Bank
    The object representing the Bank user
    BasicInterface
    Base class that all other UI interfaces can use
    Card
    The basic information for a debit/credit card
    Customer
    A customer account for standard clients
    CustomerInterface
    The frontend encapsulating all actions that can be done by a customer account
    InventoryManager
    Contains all methods for managing the inventory of a storefront
    Item
    An item is an entity that is sold in the store
    LoginManager
    Contains all the methods for interacting with the account list
    Order
    An order created by a user
    Shipment
    A class that contains an item with an amount of the item
    Supplier
    The account that suppliers use to interact with orders
    SupplierInterface
    The frontend encapsulating all actions that can be done by a supplier account
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Order.OrderStatus
    An enum containing all states for an order
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CreditLimitException
    Exception for handling when the credit limit of a card is exceeded
    InvalidAccountTypeException
    Exception for handling when trying to access non-existent properties of an account
    InvalidCardException
    Exception for handling when the card info is invalid
    InvalidLoginException
    Exception for handling when attempting to access an account with incorrect credentials
    ItemNotFoundException
    Exception for handling when trying to access an item that doesn't exist
    NoAccountFoundException
    Exception for handling when trying to access an account that doesn't exist
    OutOfStockException
    Exception for handling when trying to reserve an item that doesn't have enough stock left
    UnauthorizedException
    Exception for handling when trying access a piece of an account with without logging in
    UsernameTakenException
    Exception for handling when trying to create an account with a username that already exists
